pour la carotte.

01:08:06.206 --> 01:08:07.247
Olson ?

01:08:08.175 --> 01:08:09.216
Hank ?

01:08:10.683 --> 01:08:11.853
Olson ?

01:08:11.922 --> 01:08:13.244
